{"id":265664,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/11/维权网-北京张悦诉东城房管局拆迁行政许可案将/","date":"2012-11-28T11:45:50Z","modified":"2012-11-28T11:45:50Z","title":"维权网 | 北京张悦诉东城房管局拆迁行政许可案将开庭（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员张宁宁报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span>日</span><span>，北京市东城区法院向张悦送达了开庭传票，载明：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>日</span><span>上午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>点</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>分</span><span>在该院第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>法庭公开审理张悦诉北京市东城区房屋管理局行政许可案。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span><span>日</span><span>，住北京市崇文区革新里甲</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">19</span><span>号的张悦向北京市东城区法院起诉，请求判决撤销被告北京市东城区房屋管理局于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2010</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>日</span><span>作出京建东拆许字【</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2010</span><span>】第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>号《房屋拆迁许可证》。鼎能置业开发有限公司为本案第三人。起诉后不久，该院裁定中止诉讼，一年多后突然恢复诉讼。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>张悦在起诉状中称，被告北京市东城区房屋管理局于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2010</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>日向第三人颁发了京建东拆许字【</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2010</span><span>】第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>号《房屋拆迁许可证》，其范围为：东至原永外大街东线</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">:</span><span>南至革新南路</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">;</span><span>西至马家堡路</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">;</span><span>北至铁路。张悦认为，被告北京市东城区房屋管理局不具备作出此许可的主体资格，其行为违反建设部建法（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2004</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">154</span><span>号文件第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>条规定；该《房屋拆迁许可证》的格式和内容违背了建设部关于印制颁发《房屋拆迁许可证》的通知的规定；被告在作出该《房屋拆迁许可证》前，既没有召开听证会；也没有听取原告方的意见，违法了《行政许可法》第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">46</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">47</span><span>条规定。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>张悦希望法院排除干扰，作出公正的判决，维护法律尊严，维护拆迁受害人的合法权益。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-z6hWriKINHg/ULXUh8vUDFI/AAAAAAAAUa8/yDp6LNvp2oc/s1600/%E4%BC%A0%E7%A5%A8%E5%BC%A0%E6%82%A6.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-z6hWriKINHg/ULXUh8vUDFI/AAAAAAAAUa8/yDp6LNvp2oc/s320/%E4%BC%A0%E7%A5%A8%E5%BC%A0%E6%82%A6.jpg\" width=\"226\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-8XofqIopkQ8/ULXUlqToTLI/AAAAAAAAUbE/3qoEP10F7O0/s1600/%E5%BC%A0%E6%82%A6.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-8XofqIopkQ8/ULXUlqToTLI/AAAAAAAAUbE/3qoEP10F7O0/s320/%E5%BC%A0%E6%82%A6.jpg\" width=\"231\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-5718126284836754047?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910]}